== RelSpread

$ RelSpread(vx) = Spread(vx) / abs(Center(vx)) $

- Measures the relative dispersion of a sample to $Center(vx)$
- Pragmatic alternative to the _coefficient of variation_
- Domain: $Center(vx) != 0$
- Unit: relative

$ RelSpread(k dot vx) = RelSpread(vx) $

$ RelSpread(vx) >= 0 $
